<span id="freeTextContainer8013305374445726421">Red Gone Bad<br/>By Lucy Pireel<br/><br/>This is a fun version of ‘Red Riding Hood’ for the adult crowd. She’s the apple of her father’s overprotective eye and the object of pity to her two best friends who presume she will live out her life as a spinster. Crafty, wily, brimming with secret desires…Red is not what anyone in this story thinks she is except maybe the ‘Wolf’.<br/><br/>I don’t want to spoil this excellently written and professionally edited work of fiction for you. Rest assured I liked it enough to give it </span>
