<span id="freeTextContainer12127350883206692908">Lucy is an avid reader and writer. She doesn&apos;t limit herself to any one genre but tries to read them all. &quot;For one might be surprised if one tries something new&quot; is one of her philosophies.<br/>When she&apos;s not reading or writing, you can find her outside on a long walk, or twisted into a pretzel in some yoga pose.<br/>She loves people and interacting with readers and other writers and can be found on Google+</span>
  <span id="freeText12127350883206692908" style="display:none">Lucy is an avid reader and writer. She doesn't limit herself to any one genre but tries to read them all. "For one might be surprised if one tries something new" is one of her philosophies.<br />When she's not reading or writing, you can find her outside on a long walk, or twisted into a pretzel in some yoga pose.<br />She loves people and interacting with readers and other writers and can be found on Google+, the book of faces and many other places.</span>
